  <official_title>A Double-Blinded, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Multiple Dose Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetic, and Antiviral Activity of TD-6450, a NS5A Inhibitor, in Treatment Naïve Subjects With Genotype 1, 2 or 3 Chronic Hepatitis C Virus (HCV)</official_title>
